metadata.name: THE GATEWAY ARCH
metadata.description:
I shoot pictures therefore I exist! I've chosen to represent this existence of mine through some film photography, starting from the very early days back in 1998 until present. I hope through this body of work you will be able to see how I have evolved through my Photography and how I am experimenting from time to time. Enjoy and thank you!

- - -

Collection: PHOTOGRAPHY DAYS IN EDITIONS
